WEBVTT



00:00:08.159 --> 00:00:08.960
Guys

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:10.199
Dinner after work?

00:00:10.680 --> 00:00:11.239
Sure

00:00:16.639 --> 00:00:17.440
Guys

00:00:17.680 --> 00:00:18.680
What are we having tonight?

00:00:20.479 --> 00:00:21.600
All right, my treat

00:00:22.440 --> 00:00:22.760
Okay

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:23.520
My treat

00:00:24.959 --> 00:00:25.920
Little Lu Yi

00:00:26.639 --> 00:00:27.600
This time, your nose

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:28.799
really did a great job

00:00:29.600 --> 00:00:31.159
I was thinking

00:00:31.559 --> 00:00:32.759
your fitness test back then

00:00:32.759 --> 00:00:33.599
how did you even pass?

00:00:35.720 --> 00:00:36.959
Barely, with a low score

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:39.400
And you are proud of that?

00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:40.560
You cannot keep doing this

00:00:40.560 --> 00:00:41.840
It is so dangerous

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:43.159
You can't rely on luck forever

00:00:43.680 --> 00:00:45.479
Look how risky that Liu Ping thing was

00:00:47.319 --> 00:00:48.159
I am telling you

00:00:48.479 --> 00:00:49.799
we are Detectives

00:00:49.880 --> 00:00:50.840
who knows when

00:00:50.840 --> 00:00:52.799
we will run into some desperate criminal

00:00:54.479 --> 00:00:55.080
Lin Shen

00:00:55.680 --> 00:00:56.599
When you have time, teach her

00:00:57.520 --> 00:00:58.040
All right

00:01:03.360 --> 00:01:04.319
Then today it is

00:01:05.760 --> 00:01:06.480
Today?

00:01:06.800 --> 00:01:07.120
Let's go

00:01:07.239 --> 00:01:07.839
Lin Shen

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:09.559
Actually,

00:01:14.279 --> 00:01:14.919
in a situation like this,

00:01:14.959 --> 00:01:16.160
If you still cannot break free

00:01:16.239 --> 00:01:17.319
you need to try another way

00:01:17.440 --> 00:01:18.519
Do not fixate on what is in front of you

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:23.519
Not bad

00:01:24.160 --> 00:01:25.160
You are learning fast

00:01:25.480 --> 00:01:26.559
and using momentum when you turn

00:01:26.919 --> 00:01:28.040
Way better than last time, standing there

00:01:28.040 --> 00:01:29.599
and letting someone take you hostage

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:31.680
People

00:01:31.800 --> 00:01:32.839
have to grow up

00:01:33.120 --> 00:01:35.080
You cannot keep learning the hard way

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:37.480
True

00:01:38.639 --> 00:01:39.879
Fixating on something

00:01:41.160 --> 00:01:42.519
is not always a good thing

00:01:58.480 --> 00:01:59.239
Lin Shen

00:02:01.319 --> 00:02:02.199
This morning

00:02:02.239 --> 00:02:03.879
who was the person you visited at the cemetery?

00:02:08.839 --> 00:02:09.639
You tailed me?

00:02:11.759 --> 00:02:12.839
Answer my question

00:02:15.639 --> 00:02:16.679
That is my private business

00:02:17.240 --> 00:02:18.039
It has nothing to do with you

00:02:21.160 --> 00:02:22.000
That person

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:24.360
is the one in my dad's notebook

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:25.639
the person in that photo

00:02:26.199 --> 00:02:28.199
You carry that photo with you every day

00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:30.320
and you say it is none of my business?

00:02:35.039 --> 00:02:35.639
Lu Yi

00:02:35.880 --> 00:02:36.839
Under the recusal rule

00:02:36.839 --> 00:02:38.399
as Lu Yong's immediate family

00:02:38.399 --> 00:02:39.240
you should not

00:02:39.240 --> 00:02:40.240
have anything to do with this case

00:02:40.800 --> 00:02:41.479
Those are the rules

00:02:44.800 --> 00:02:45.440
Lin Shen

00:02:46.520 --> 00:02:47.639
I treat you like a friend

00:02:47.639 --> 00:02:48.919
I have been nothing but sincere with you

00:02:48.919 --> 00:02:50.559
and now you are using rules to pressure me

00:02:50.759 --> 00:02:52.960
As your friend, I am protecting you

00:02:53.759 --> 00:02:55.000
Lu Yi, you have no idea what this case...

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:56.279
What kind of friend is that, Lin Shen?

00:02:56.520 --> 00:02:57.199
Do I have any friends?

00:02:57.199 --> 00:02:58.559
Do you think I have friends?

00:03:00.679 --> 00:03:01.800
Am I not?

00:03:02.600 --> 00:03:03.679
What kind of friend are you?

00:03:04.880 --> 00:03:06.759
A friend would know why my dad is in a coma

00:03:06.759 --> 00:03:08.440
but refuse to tell me a single word?

00:03:08.919 --> 00:03:10.520
A friend would use the cold word "rules"

00:03:10.520 --> 00:03:11.679
to shut me down?

00:03:12.039 --> 00:03:13.039
A friend would, in the middle of the night

00:03:13.039 --> 00:03:14.039
guard against me like I am a thief?

00:03:14.039 --> 00:03:14.960
Leave without telling me?

00:03:14.960 --> 00:03:16.240
Is that a friend, Lin Shen?

00:03:23.919 --> 00:03:24.679
Lu Yi

00:03:34.320 --> 00:03:34.839
Fine

00:03:35.839 --> 00:03:36.600
I get it

00:03:39.320 --> 00:03:40.320
I was kidding myself

00:03:43.800 --> 00:03:44.440
Lu Yi

00:03:45.160 --> 00:03:45.679
Lu Yi

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:15.800
And this one here

00:04:15.839 --> 00:04:17.000
is from our unit

00:04:17.040 --> 00:04:17.880
the most beautiful

00:04:18.239 --> 00:04:19.200
and the most capable

00:04:19.200 --> 00:04:21.079
and the Detective I am closest to, Officer Lin

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:21.720
Lin Shen

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:24.279
Stop chasing me

00:04:24.359 --> 00:04:25.399
Am I that adorable?

00:04:26.559 --> 00:04:28.480
You are really good at pretending

00:04:28.480 --> 00:04:30.160
Besides money and food

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:31.679
can you think of anything else?

00:04:32.279 --> 00:04:33.720
And thinking of you

00:04:34.279 --> 00:04:34.600
What?

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:35.079
Come here

00:04:35.079 --> 00:04:35.600
Don't come over

00:04:35.920 --> 00:04:37.079
Once you have me

00:04:37.320 --> 00:04:38.600
you will get used to it

00:04:39.359 --> 00:04:39.880
Have you ever gotten

00:04:39.880 --> 00:04:40.679
from someone

00:04:40.679 --> 00:04:41.920
a special gift?

00:04:42.200 --> 00:04:43.720
Happy birthday, Lin Shen

00:04:44.239 --> 00:04:46.200
I am your best friend

00:04:48.200 --> 00:04:49.279
Carry me to the car

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:51.200
I do not ask for much

00:04:51.440 --> 00:04:52.160
Just like this

00:04:52.399 --> 00:04:53.160
a bridal carry

00:04:53.160 --> 00:04:53.640
How about it?

00:04:53.640 --> 00:04:54.480
What is wrong with you?

00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:56.640
Are you crazy?

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:06.959
Why are you not drinking?

00:05:07.239 --> 00:05:08.359
Come on, drink

00:05:09.320 --> 00:05:09.920
No

00:05:10.320 --> 00:05:11.480
These are my own people

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:12.720
No need to hide anything

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:13.760
Lin Shen

00:05:15.799 --> 00:05:17.399
You are my best friend

00:05:17.760 --> 00:05:18.679
Listen to me

00:05:19.399 --> 00:05:20.239
Hold on tight to me

00:05:35.679 --> 00:05:36.359
Sis Shen

00:05:37.440 --> 00:05:38.160
Haozi

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:39.880
What are you doing here?

00:05:40.880 --> 00:05:41.799
Let me tell you a secret

00:05:42.440 --> 00:05:43.559
My family owns this place

00:05:58.239 --> 00:05:59.079
You two fought?

00:06:04.880 --> 00:06:05.480
No

00:06:06.079 --> 00:06:06.760
Sis Shen

00:06:06.959 --> 00:06:08.200
We have worked together for so long

00:06:08.200 --> 00:06:09.239
You think I do not know you?

00:06:15.079 --> 00:06:15.959
If you can argue

00:06:16.200 --> 00:06:17.000
it means you both

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.279
still matter to each other

00:06:18.679 --> 00:06:19.679
A real break

00:06:19.880 --> 00:06:21.399
is always silent

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:25.040
Having a friend who makes you ignore personal gain

00:06:25.399 --> 00:06:26.440
and who you aren't afraid to argue with

00:06:26.920 --> 00:06:27.959
is really rare

00:06:28.799 --> 00:06:29.880
Lu Yi is that kind of person

00:06:30.480 --> 00:06:31.440
So are you

00:06:32.640 --> 00:06:34.200
If one day you stop arguing

00:06:34.640 --> 00:06:36.320
and get polite like ordinary friends

00:06:36.880 --> 00:06:38.040
then it's really Darn it

00:06:43.880 --> 00:06:44.799
You're treating today

00:06:45.000 --> 00:06:45.720
No problem

00:08:11.839 --> 00:08:12.720
Officer

00:08:13.200 --> 00:08:14.119
Something terrible happened

00:08:15.040 --> 00:08:16.239
At the pig farm in the western suburbs

00:08:16.839 --> 00:08:18.160
someone got gnawed by pigs

00:08:32.119 --> 00:08:32.640
Captain Duan

00:08:32.840 --> 00:08:34.799
Someone got gnawed by pigs at the west farm

00:08:36.239 --> 00:08:37.200
What's going on

00:08:37.679 --> 00:08:38.799
Gnawed by pigs

00:08:54.400 --> 00:08:56.200
What kind of sin is that

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:57.000
What's the situation

00:08:57.760 --> 00:08:59.239
She really was eaten by pigs

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:03.239
Judging by the damage at the scene

00:09:03.239 --> 00:09:04.280
and the remains left behind

00:09:04.520 --> 00:09:06.400
pigs did gnaw on the victim

00:09:06.919 --> 00:09:08.039
Pigs are omnivores

00:09:08.640 --> 00:09:09.880
Attacking and gnawing humans

00:09:09.880 --> 00:09:11.039
isn't impossible

00:09:11.159 --> 00:09:11.919
especially when a person

00:09:11.919 --> 00:09:13.479
has lost the ability to resist

00:09:14.599 --> 00:09:15.640
But the specifics

00:09:15.799 --> 00:09:17.280
require a further autopsy

00:09:18.719 --> 00:09:20.000
There are several breaks in the fence

00:09:20.119 --> 00:09:21.760
but no obvious signs of forced entry

00:09:22.719 --> 00:09:23.960
There's an overturned bucket nearby

00:09:23.960 --> 00:09:25.359
and some scattered pig feed

00:09:27.320 --> 00:09:28.799
An accidental fall seems more likely

00:09:29.799 --> 00:09:30.200
Sir

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:31.760
What am I supposed to do

00:09:31.880 --> 00:09:32.599
Sir

00:09:33.359 --> 00:09:34.599
When did you last see your wife

00:09:34.599 --> 00:09:35.320
exactly

00:09:35.719 --> 00:09:36.479
What was she doing

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:38.320
Last night

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:39.640
Last night

00:09:39.640 --> 00:09:40.119
Write that down

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:42.239
She even warmed me a pot of liquor

00:09:44.479 --> 00:09:45.400
It's okay, take your time

00:09:45.400 --> 00:09:46.039
Take your time

00:09:47.000 --> 00:09:48.159
This morning when I got up

00:09:48.599 --> 00:09:50.119
I was here feeding the pigs

00:09:50.119 --> 00:09:51.960
and I saw that shoe

00:09:52.039 --> 00:09:52.840
Sir

00:09:53.400 --> 00:09:54.159
Sir

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:57.799
Was your wife in poor health

00:09:59.679 --> 00:10:01.840
Her eyesight was bad

00:10:03.039 --> 00:10:03.919
Her joints hurt

00:10:03.919 --> 00:10:05.679
Everything hurt

00:10:06.039 --> 00:10:08.359
She wasn't steady on her feet either

00:10:12.679 --> 00:10:14.159
Then did you and the neighbors

00:10:14.159 --> 00:10:15.479
have any conflict

00:10:15.479 --> 00:10:16.520
any disputes, that sort of thing

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:17.840
You can't go in here

00:10:19.359 --> 00:10:20.400
In this ravine

00:10:20.400 --> 00:10:21.000
Old Zhao

00:10:21.320 --> 00:10:21.919
Old Zhao

00:10:22.359 --> 00:10:22.960
Old Zhao

00:10:24.359 --> 00:10:25.239
What's going on

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:31.599
Xiao Hu

00:10:36.200 --> 00:10:37.119
Your auntie

00:10:37.640 --> 00:10:38.799
is gone

00:10:38.840 --> 00:10:39.960
How could she be gone

00:10:42.119 --> 00:10:43.359
She fell into the pigpen

00:10:43.559 --> 00:10:45.280
and those beasts gnawed her

00:10:45.320 --> 00:10:46.159
Help him over there

00:10:46.719 --> 00:10:47.159
Okay

00:10:47.520 --> 00:10:48.280
Sir, let's go back and sit for a bit

00:10:48.280 --> 00:10:49.080
Who are you

00:10:49.080 --> 00:10:49.679
Officer

00:10:49.679 --> 00:10:50.599
What's your relationship to him

00:10:50.960 --> 00:10:53.000
I've known Old Zhao for many years

00:10:53.479 --> 00:10:54.520
Their pigs

00:10:54.520 --> 00:10:56.440
mostly supply our shop

00:10:57.359 --> 00:10:58.200
His wife

00:10:58.359 --> 00:10:59.239
had bad legs

00:10:59.640 --> 00:11:01.080
She always fell when walking

00:11:01.520 --> 00:11:02.400
I never thought

00:11:04.479 --> 00:11:05.400
Cigarette?

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:06.559
No

00:11:06.559 --> 00:11:07.280
It's fine

00:11:07.280 --> 00:11:08.000
Come on, come on

00:11:08.799 --> 00:11:09.840
How many years have you known him

00:11:11.359 --> 00:11:12.840
Quite a few years, I guess

00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:14.080
I don't remember

00:11:15.599 --> 00:11:16.400
Well, um

00:11:16.719 --> 00:11:18.320
Do you know how their family

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:19.960
got along with the people around them

00:11:21.080 --> 00:11:22.559
I'm not really sure

00:11:23.799 --> 00:11:25.320
With things blowing up like this today

00:11:25.320 --> 00:11:26.799
I can't take pigs in anymore

00:11:27.559 --> 00:11:28.200
Old Zhao

00:11:28.559 --> 00:11:29.599
My condolences.

00:11:30.239 --> 00:11:31.080
I'm leaving

00:11:52.479 --> 00:11:53.919
The autopsy report is out

00:11:53.919 --> 00:11:55.760
The victim's injuries were not caused

00:11:55.760 --> 00:11:56.760
by an accidental fall,

00:11:56.760 --> 00:11:57.559
but by blunt-force trauma.

00:11:57.559 --> 00:11:58.320
That means

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:00.679
she didn't accidentally fall into the pigpen

00:12:01.200 --> 00:12:02.760
she was murdered first

00:12:02.760 --> 00:12:04.119
then dumped into the pigpen

00:12:04.520 --> 00:12:05.080
Yes

00:12:05.719 --> 00:12:06.760
I suggest we conduct

00:12:06.919 --> 00:12:07.919
a second search of Old Zhao's place

00:12:08.039 --> 00:12:09.440
If needed, we can run a polygraph

00:12:17.840 --> 00:12:18.479
Bro Lei

00:12:19.000 --> 00:12:20.159
What's up with those two now

00:12:20.359 --> 00:12:21.239
They're having a spat

00:12:21.919 --> 00:12:22.719
Leave it alone

00:12:23.359 --> 00:12:25.239
Lu Yi must've pissed off my Xiao Shen

00:12:30.599 --> 00:12:30.960
Thirsty?

00:12:30.960 --> 00:12:31.840
Want an apple?

00:12:32.039 --> 00:12:32.679
I'm allergic

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:34.280
This old man is definitely suspicious

00:12:35.320 --> 00:12:36.719
And the grief he showed

00:12:36.719 --> 00:12:37.760
didn't seem real

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:40.559
For a man nearly 70,

00:12:41.159 --> 00:12:42.760
could he really kill his wife

00:12:42.760 --> 00:12:44.200
and dump her into the pigpen?

00:12:45.039 --> 00:12:46.760
Where would he get the nerve and strength?